    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduction to Hatch-Fancy-Pypi-Readme Module</title>

      <para>
        <application>Hatch-Fancy-Pypi-Readme</application> is a hatch plugin
        filling the readme field into the metadata of a Python module from
        markup language documentation files of the module.
      </para>

      &lfs123_checked;

