    <sect3 role="installation">
      <title>Installation of Hatch-Fancy-Pypi-Readme</title>

    <para>Build the module: </para>

&build-wheel;

    <para>
      Now, as the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> user:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>&install-wheel; hatch-fancy-pypi-readme</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      To test the installation, make sure <xref linkend='pytest'/> is
      installed and run:
    </para>

<screen remap="test"><userinput>python3 -m venv --system-site-packages testenv            &amp;&amp;
testenv/bin/pip3 install 'hatch-fancy-pypi-readme[tests]' &amp;&amp;
testenv/bin/python -m pytest</userinput></screen>

    </sect3>

